        <name>Esquina El Watusi</name>
        <description>Tony had drinks with Hermes Ayala, freelance journalist for outlets including Vice and HuffPost; Laura Moscoso, journalist specializing in data visualization and multimedia.</description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1517-C2185B</styleUrl>
        <Point>
