      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Casa Vieja</name>
        <description><![CDATA[Tony had a meal with Liza Fournier Cordova, a teacher. They had corn fritters with ham; plantain soup; pastel al caldero, or "pork marinated in bitter orange, taro root, green plantains, squash, and garbanzo beans, slow cooked"; morcilla (blood sausage).]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1577-C2185B</styleUrl>
        <Point>
