          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Salvemos a Playuela</name>
        <description><![CDATA[Tony met with activist "Pocho" to have  a feast of Sancocho, a beef stew with yuca, plantains; fresh-caught grouper and red snapper.]]></description>
