        <name>Pacific Inn Pub</name>
        <description><![CDATA[Tony had fish & chips with Astra Elane and Dustin Patterson, members of local band The Gods Themselves.]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1577-C2185B</styleUrl>
        <Point>
