      <Placemark>
        <name><![CDATA[Dolmama - Armenia's Restaurant]]></name>
        <description><![CDATA["This is what my soul needed,” Tony said as he ate braised lamb shank with rice pilaf; vegetable manti ]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1577-C2185B</styleUrl>
