      <Placemark>
        <name>Meal with locals</name>
        <description>Tony visited Mariam Movsisyan’s grandmother’s family home. They had ghapama (traditional dish consisting of a baked pumpkin or squash stuffed with rice, nuts, raisins, and apricots), Armenian cheese and lavash, hummus.</description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1603-9C27B0</styleUrl>
        <Point>
