        <name>China Cafe</name>
        <description>Tony and photojournalist Simon Go ordered Fried pork cutlet over rice with tomato sauce, soup with macaroni, spam and egg, French toast with peanut butter and condensed milk, pineapple bun.</description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1577-C2185B</styleUrl>
        <Point>
