          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Michelberger Hotel</name>
        <description>Tony ate at the restaurant in this hotel with Ellen Allien, famous Berlin DJ. They had sausage made from chicken, pig’s feet, and sage with smoked potatoes and apple; braised beef shoulder served with root vegetables, potatoes, horseradish, and kale.</description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1577-AFB42B</styleUrl>
