      <Placemark>
        <name>Meal with locals</name>
        <description><![CDATA[Tony had a meal at Anton Newcombe's studio (frontman of the Brian Jonestown Massacre) and friends. The had roasted lamb, sweet potatoes, and homemade schnapps.]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1603-9C27B0</styleUrl>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
