      <name>Season 12</name>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Unknown small restaurants</name>
        <description>Tony met up with W. Kamau Bell in the capital city. They had a lunch of grilled tilapia, ugali, Tusker beer. Tony also had beers with Njeri Gikera, owner of ChilliMango clothing store; Melissa Mbugua, managing partner at MNM Consulting Africa; and Bell at another local place.</description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1577-C2185B</styleUrl>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            37.906193,-0.023559,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
