        <name><![CDATA[Ca'Laura]]></name>
        <description>Tony and Chef José Andrés at this plaza café. They had arvejas (green peas) with ham, croquette, mussels, steak topped with blue cheese</description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1577-C2185B</styleUrl>
        <Point>
