      <Placemark>
        <name>Sobrecueva</name>
        <description><![CDATA[Tony and José Andrés had Cabrales (a type of blue cheese) at this cheese farm. José commented that the cheese had penicillin in it and Tony's retort was, "I can feel my syphilis clearing already!" ]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1566-9C27B0</styleUrl>
